data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in a tranquil cul-de-sac, where luxury and comfort seamlessly blend. This exquisite 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath residence offers the perfect balance of modern elegance and cozy charm. Quartz Countertops in Kitchen, LVP flooring, Cozy fireplace in Living room, Formal dining space, Additional Breakfast Dinning space, Relaxing sunroom with vaulted ceiling! Step outside into your own outdoor oasis – a haven for both relaxation and entertainment. Stamped concrete, Covered Patio, with outdoor fire pit Fenced in backyard, Green giant Arborvitae Trees which provide full privacy, perfect for hosting events and watching games with friends, on a cul-de-sac that provides privacy! An additional Storage Room, Jetted Tub, also includes a one year of Home Warranty which Covers AC unit & Heat Boiler, all Appliances. Tour this Amazing House Today. This home is everything you are looking for!
